name: Roboto Factory - Part Nine
description:
Our prototype designer: Norma Xelda Jara very creative and with a lot of adrenaline for the success of her series the droid has communicated with her social networks to inform us of her new project. With full support of the DAO of Roboto Inc. and after weeks of intensive work with full cooperation of the workers.
Today the press and family members were invited to a "Vodka party" to inaugurate the collectible series: "Tribute" which will soon go on sale @WorldRobotDay Celebrate #Robots on the 25th January, the  2nd #WorldRobotDay #softrobotics
He comments: "We are currently in beta mode, testing all the electronic circuits and polishing some anatomical details. Our intention is a commitment to surprise our buyers".
She was very happy as she sipped her vodka.
